<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Withdrawal Request Received</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .logo {
            max-width: 150px;
            height: auto;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .content {
            background: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .highlight-box {
            background: #e3f2fd;
            border-left: 4px solid #2196F3;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .amount {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #1565c0;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #2196F3;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .details {
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .detail-row {
            display: flex;
            margin: 10px 0;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
        }
        .detail-label {
            flex: 1;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .detail-value {
            flex: 2;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <img src="<%= logoUrl || 'https://via.placeholder.com/150' %>" alt="<%= appName %>" class="logo">
        <h2>Withdrawal Request Received</h2>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <p>Hello <%= name %>,</p>
        
        <p>We've received your request to withdraw your affiliate earnings. Here are the details:</p>
        
        <div class="highlight-box">
            <p style="margin: 0; text-align: center;">
                <span style="font-size: 14px;">Withdrawal Amount</span><br>
                <span class="amount">$<%= amount %></span>
            </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="details">
            <div class="detail-row">
                <div class="detail-label">Payment Method:</div>
                <div class="detail-value"><%= paymentMethod %></div>
            </div>
            <div class="detail-row">
                <div class="detail-label">Request Date:</div>
                <div class="detail-value"><%= requestDate %></div>
            </div>
            <div class="detail-row">
                <div class="detail-label">Status:</div>
                <div class="detail-value"><strong>Pending Approval</strong></div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <p>Our team is currently processing your request. Most withdrawal requests are processed within 3-5 business days, but it may take longer depending on your payment method.</p>
        
        <p>You'll receive another email once your withdrawal has been processed. If we need any additional information to complete your request, we'll contact you using the email associated with your account.</p>
        
        <div style="text-align: center; margin: 25px 0;">
            <a href="<%= dashboardUrl %>" class="button">View Withdrawal Status</a>
        </div>
        
        <p>If you didn't initiate this withdrawal or believe this is an error, please contact our support team immediately.</p>
        
        <p>Best regards,<br>
        The <%= appName %> Team</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>Â© <%= currentYear %> <%= appName %>. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
